{"id":585249,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【立此存照】网民热捧抨修宪教授著作后，豆瓣删/","date":"2018-05-23T07:33:20Z","modified":"2018-05-23T10:17:37Z","title":"【立此存照】网民热捧抨修宪教授著作后，豆瓣删除相关条目","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>中南财经政法大学女副教授翟桔红近日<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/%e4%bc%98%e5%be%8b%e5%ba%93-%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%89%e4%b8%80%e5%a5%b3%e5%89%af%e6%95%99%e6%8e%88%e6%8a%a8%e4%bf%ae%e5%ae%aa%e9%81%ad%e5%bc%80%e9%99%a4%e5%85%9a%e7%b1%8d/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">因在课堂上批评修宪而被开除党籍</a>、并被学校建议“调离教学科研岗位”“发证机关取消其教师资格”，引起舆论一片哗然。不少网民前往豆瓣，为其著作《违宪审查与民主制的平衡》打出高分以示声援。豆瓣随后删除了相关条目。《违宪审查与民主制的平衡》出版于2012年，为武汉大学“985工程”二期拓展项目“政治文明与民主政治建设研究”的重要任务之一《民主与政治文明研究丛书》的一部分。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_585259\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-585259\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821-300x155.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821-768x397.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/IMG_4821-1024x529.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">副教授翟桔红因在课堂上批评修宪而被开除后，其著作《违宪审查与民主制的平衡》在豆瓣评分曾一度达到10分，后该书页面遭删除；网络图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_585262\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-585262\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1412\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339.jpg 1456w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339-106x300.jpg 106w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339-768x2169.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059213339-363x1024.jpg 363w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《违宪审查与民主制的平衡》一书豆瓣短评截图；该书豆瓣页面已被删除</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附：《违宪审查与民主制的平衡》第五章、第四节《对中国建构违宪审查制度的启示》</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059302187.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585250\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059302187.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"657\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059302187.jpg 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/1-e1527059302187-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/2-e1527059329288.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585251\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/2-e1527059329288.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"646\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/2-e1527059329288.jpg 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/2-e1527059329288-232x300.jpg 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3-e1527059363860.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585252\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3-e1527059363860.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"634\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3-e1527059363860.jpg 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/3-e1527059363860-237x300.jpg 237w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/4-e1527059393910.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585253\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltime